    <sect3 role="package">
      <title>Introduction to Py3c</title>

      <para>
        <application>Py3c</application> helps you port C extensions to
        Python 3. It provides a detailed guide, and a set of macros to
        make porting easy and reduce boilerplate.
      </para>

      &lfs110a_checked;

